{"tid":2006737,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"分餅仔拒招標 林鄭政府慣技","createTime":"2020-05-08T03:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T03:59:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66b879d3253c48933281d78804c7a620a8fc5590","tid":2006737,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/TJXQO73WUQLU5WQYAURTQG66LE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FTJXQO73WUQLU5WQYAURTQG66LE%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0NKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=85f9fe09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FTJXQO73WUQLU5WQYAURTQG66LE%2F&h=21088135\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/TJXQO73WUQLU5WQYAURTQG66LE/</a><br />\n<br />\n分餅仔拒招標 林鄭政府慣技<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588870103_36cf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588870103_36cf.gif&h=0fb89bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥2018年出席龍達工廠開幕禮。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府無招標直接指派「友好」商家接單，是林鄭政府的慣技。2015年政府計劃活化尖沙嘴海濱，便在零諮詢下直接「欽點」新世界擴建星光大道，觸怒其他發展商一度入稟提司法覆核。擴建計劃最終觸礁，當局跪低改以簡約方式翻新星光大道，項目更收回由康文署管理，不再交新世界負責。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高官倘誤導公眾屬行為失當<br />\n<br />\n故宮館被轟黑箱作業<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥2016年底出任政務司司長身兼西九文化區董事局主席期間，處理西九興建故宮文化博物館項目時，亦遭批評黑箱作。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至近期政府興建隔離中心設施，工程亦被揭發刻意避開招標，6項涉及鯉魚門公園及度假村、八鄉少訊中心及竹篙灣的檢疫中心等相關工程，5項以「直接委聘」方式批。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"1719b2b9270d376662d7cedab3fd4f919cfde412","tid":2006737,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4cfdadbf6179b8cd23ae51ed5fd5efeac244f85","tid":2006737,"uid":43527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"早幾年都仲可以jr    而家有哂證據都未必得"}]}